0.title: Host CPU usage %
0.query:
timeseries avg(dt.cloud.vmware.hypervisor.cpu.usage), by: { dt.entity.hypervisor }
| fieldsAdd cloud.vmware.hypervisor.cpu.usage = ArrayAvg(`avg(dt.cloud.vmware.hypervisor.cpu.usage)`)
| sort cloud.vmware.hypervisor.cpu.usage desc
| limit 20
